thread.title: Wayne Sweeney
thread.title_full: California Casualty Auto and Home Insurance reviewed by Wayne Sweeney

author: Wayne Sweeney
title: Wayne Sweeney
text: California Casualty is the best insurance company I have ever been with. For sixteen years, when I call, I speak to a person. The few times I have needed them, they were there immediately. Always a positive resolution. I recommend them.
